<emphasis box="[916,996,1589,1606]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="59">Cordaites</emphasis>
cf. 
<emphasis box="[1027,1106,1589,1606]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="59">lingulatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Grand’Eury, transverse section of lamina (SAR24B4L07); 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[488,502,1612,1629]" pageId="16" pageNumber="59">G</emphasis>
, transverse section of three small radially symmetrical ovules showing three sutures (arrows) of the sclerotesta (SAR47A1B01); 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[468,482,1635,1652]" pageId="16" pageNumber="59">H</emphasis>
, 
