(Brongniart) Renault
</taxonomicName>
, transverse section of the ovule (SAR15BT01); 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[238,244,1657,1674]" pageId="16" pageNumber="59">I</emphasis>
, cf. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Z.M.Li" authorityYear="1993" box="[283,436,1657,1674]" class="Pinopsida" family="Cordaitales (awaiting allocation)" genus="Parataxospermum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Cordaitales" pageId="16" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[283,436,1657,1674]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="59">Parataxospermum</emphasis>
